<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> ka<hi rend="grantha">sari</hi> parmma<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>kku yāṇṭu <hi rend="grantha">1<unclear>8</unclear></hi><g type="dash"/>Āvatu tirupparā<supplied reason="omitted">y</supplied>ttuṟaip perumāṉaṭikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kā<hi rend="grantha">ryya</hi> m Ārā<supplied reason="omitted">y</supplied>kiṉṟa <hi rend="grantha">Ādi</hi> ttapaṭārar
<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> ttuṟaipperumāṉaṭikaḷ mutaley koṇṭu Aṭṭuvitta kuttuviḷakku pattumāy
<lb n="3"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> Āyirattu Aññūṟṟu <unclear>pala ce</unclear>yyu
</p>

<p>By the side of this are the following fragments—</p>

<!--<h4><hi rend="italic">First section.</hi></h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>veṭṭiy maṟṟum Eppeṟpaṭṭatum kāttukkuṭuppomā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṉom naṉṉalūr Ūrālicainta Ūrom Itu <hi rend="grantha">pa</hi> ṉ<hi rend="grantha">mā</hi>
<lb n="3" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">heśva<supplied reason="omitted">ra</supplied> rakṣai</hi>
</p>

<!--<h4><hi rend="italic">Second section.</hi></h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>ṇi ku <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ṟkkum Ivviraṇṭu kiṭkkaiy nilamum Ippaṭi ki <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> kuvatu Ikoyilin kiḻai tirunaṉtavānattu ṉān 
<lb n="2"/>vaiypitta teṅkiṟ Aiñpatu teṅku vicatiṭai y Āka vaiy<supplied reason="omitted">t</supplied>ten maṟṟaiy niṉṟa teṅku tirumeypūccu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>kkum maṟṟu tevarkku veṇṭum vicatiṭai Āka ceytu kuṭu<supplied reason="omitted">t</supplied>t<unclear>e</unclear>n Uṟaiyūr<supplied reason="omitted">k</supplied> kūṟṟa<supplied reason="omitted">t</supplied>tu <hi rend="grantha">brahma</hi> teyam Īcānamaṅkalattu pāra
<lb n="4" break="no"/>tāyaṉ kaṇṭa ṉāccaṉāṉa pūḻiyaṉ <hi rend="grantha">brahmamārā</hi> yaṉ Iññi<supplied reason="omitted">la</supplied>ttāl van<supplied reason="omitted">ta</supplied> Iṟaiyum Eccoṟum
</p>

<!--<h4><hi rend="italic">Third section.</hi></h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>ta nilamāvatu Uṟaiyūr<supplied reason="omitted">k</supplied>kū<supplied reason="omitted">ṟṟa</supplied>ttu nānalūr Ūrom viṟṟukkuṭutta nilamāvatu ki<supplied reason="omitted">ḻ</supplied>pāṟkellaiy palāṟṟukku me<supplied reason="omitted">ṟ</supplied>kkum tenpāṟkellai tuṟaiyūr
<lb n="2" break="no"/>uṭaiyān nilattu<supplied reason="omitted">k</supplied>ku vaṭakku melpāṟkollai Ūrāṟicca Araimāvukku kiḻakku vaṭapāṟkollai Itevar tirumuḷaippuḻuticce<supplied reason="omitted">yk</supplied>kut teṟkum I
<lb n="3" break="no"/>vvicaitta perunāṉkellaiyiṟ Uṇṇilam Oḻivinṟi Itan<unclear>mi</unclear>tu poy Iraṇṭā nilattu Icai<supplied reason="omitted">n</supplied>ta kiḻpāṟkollai tirumuḷaippuḻuti<supplied reason="omitted">c</supplied> ce<supplied reason="omitted">y</supplied>kku
<lb n="4"/>meṟku teṟpāṟkellai kayattu viranākan Iraṇṭumāvukku vaṭa<supplied reason="omitted">k</supplied>ku melpāṟkellai nakkikālu<unclear>kku</unclear> kiḻakku vaṭapāṟkellai nakkikālukku
</p>

